Class XRayMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • Hospital.Machine.Machine
      • Hospital.Machine.XRayMachine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MachineAbstractFactory, Unmovable, Schedulable

    public class XRayMachine
extends Machine
implements MachineAbstractFactory
    X-ray machine used in medical tests The XRaymachine is self-replicating, a new XRayMachine can always be made from it's own object.
